                  "pageTitle": "Sure Footed",
                  "pageId": 122560,
                  "revisionId": 2663929,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Includes resistance from Shield Lancer 's shield attack, Scorpion 's tether attack, Ancient 's charge attack and tether attack, Corpus Laser Barriers , Bombard rocket explosions and Arson / Caustic Eximus' fire blasts."
